<p>DBs in conjunction with the authorization system provide strong isolation between different namespaces. Also, it should be possible to extend the authorization system to the two-part-name-access case that you described above (e.g. <a href="https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-3047" class="external-link" rel="nofollow">HIVE-3047</a>).</p>

